{"tid":278144,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"林敏驄遲開騷近1小時   全場觀眾向他爆粗","createTime":"2017-06-10T08:08:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-10T12:09:14.000Z","uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0f4c3a112e82df536b99587f568b490231f07559","tid":278144,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T08:08:54.000Z","msg":"《今天星閃閃時日如飛林敏驄35年腦交戰作品展演唱會》今晚21:23正式開騷，相比平日紅館演唱會遲足近1小時。主角林敏驄以演唱會宣傳海報的鬍鬚造型示人，白色西裝、長髮，手持電結他，出場時輕鬆向全場觀眾揮手，然後結他Solo表演。之後太極六子上台埋位，與林敏驄一齊Jam歌，所有藝人登場，暫時都不是經由肇事舞台升降上來。<br />\n<br />\n林敏驄之後開腔問全場觀眾，他說：「係未等咗好耐？係未有少少不滿？」，全場觀眾齊聲答「係﹗」，林敏驄唔知死再問：「畀一個形容詞形容現在心情？」，整個紅館觀眾即時向他爆粗﹗林敏驄說：「咁粗魯，咁都得，其實下午發生一單非工業意外，衷心希望同事無事﹗」<br />\n<img src=\"http://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170609/s00007/8413fd23e26da1c731637c3b539ecaad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170609%2Fs00007%2F8413fd23e26da1c731637c3b539ecaad.jpg&h=5a3cbc55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170609/s00007/1497017702389\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170609%2Fs00007%2F1497017702389&d=vCgATC7UJM1bjoNEo%2FwUYJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=75503e0a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170609%2Fs00007%2F1497017702389&h=fb5a1371\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170609/s00007/1497017702389</a>"},{"pid":"2ef571d415a70de1b100cc5d7c644811419d2ebf","tid":278144,"uid":46435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T08:11:57.000Z","msg":"呀Bob真係唔得罪得"},{"pid":"a6eadeb7d50b60f11310e66c4850e9b4e269c9bc","tid":278144,"uid":43861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T08:16:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呀Bob真係唔得罪得</blockquote><br />\n下"},{"pid":"195111b919f3f73b50517bc9c9fe9554c87e4ea9","tid":278144,"uid":45591,